name: Corrupted Data (Binaural)
description:
Dr Malware viruses hacking Bach's music databases. 
Artificial intelligences passes Baroque music through glitch, chiptune, chopping, noise, collage, 8bit, and binaural processes.
Polyphony at its finest: collage glitch noisy electro experimentation. 
Binaural music (8d) HEAR with headphones.
